  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a registry of renal cancer patients treated with Nexavar. It aims to evaluate
      the actual dosing of Nexavar in &quot;real-life&quot; setting vs. the prescribed dose.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
